### ############################################################
### AUTOMATION TESTS - PROACTIVE LOGIC
### ############################################################

@autoCampId = 1
@autoResourceTypeId = 1
@autoRecordedBy = 3

### [INV-AUTO-01] Trigger Low Stock with DAILY_RATION movement
### Expected: trigger an automated INVENTORY_ALERT notification.
### Note: the demo-expected title is "Alerta de inventario bajo".
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/camp-inventory/{{autoCampId}}/{{autoResourceTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minimumAlertAmount": "999999.00"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory-movements
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campId": {{autoCampId}},
  "resourceTypeId": {{autoResourceTypeId}},
  "amount": "1",
  "movementType": "DAILY_RATION",
  "sourceType": "AUTO_TEST",
  "recordedBy": {{autoRecordedBy}},
  "description": "INV-AUTO-01 trigger"
}

###

### [INV-AUTO-02] Verify audience: Admin and Resource receive INVENTORY_ALERT
### [INV-AUTO-02-A] SYSTEM_ADMIN inbox
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?type=INVENTORY_ALERT&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [INV-AUTO-02-B] RESOURCE_MANAGEMENT inbox
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?type=INVENTORY_ALERT&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}

###